  • java.lang.Object
    • mavlc.syntax.AstNodeBaseVisitor<RetTy,​ArgTy>
  • Type Parameters:
    RetTy - Return type used by visitor methods.

    All Implemented Interfaces:
    AstNodeVisitor<RetTy,​ArgTy>

    public class AstNodeBaseVisitor<RetTy,​ArgTy>
extends java.lang.Object
implements AstNodeVisitor<RetTy,​ArgTy>
    Basic visitor implementation. Each visit method calls the visit method of the corresponding super type.
